text: Hermenegildo Martínez (born 13 August 1937) is a Spanish gymnast. He competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Melilla
